    "Ruckman, Dr. Peter S_": "can be applied to Christ, or to the Jewish remnant, or to David `[char_David_Rut_4]` personally, or for that matter to Lester Roloff, Harlan Popov, Richard Wurmbrand, John `[char_John_Ref]` Huss, Martin Luther, Alex Dunlap, Jack Chick, Jerry Falwell, Jesse Helms, J. Edgar Hoover, Oliver North, or J. Frank Norris. There is nothing \u201cout of date\u201d about the Bible.",
